A LIST OF THE EXISTING SHOPS IN EACH DISTRICT
(If you make a new shop, please add it to this list)

CARAVAN DISTRICT
_______________________________________________________________
General Store - Anthios' (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/shop/gshop.c)
   A shop where players may buy/sell equipment.
Money-Changer - Turale's (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/shop/mchange.c)
   A bank where players may exchange and keep money.
Food&Booze shop - Jenn's (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/shop/jeinn.c)
   A combination inn/restaurant.
Dealer's Store - Pendras (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/lot/s16.c)
   An equipment shop (i.e. Backpacks, sacks, torches, etc.)
Mapmaker's - Ystof (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/shop/mmshop.c)
   A place where players may buy maps of the city & surroundings.
The Perfume Shop - Amey (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/shop/perfume_shop.c)
   A place to buy perfumes/colognes that remove dirtiness.

TRADESMEN'S DISTRICT
_______________________________________________________________
Weapon shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/weapon_shop.c)
   Sells low hit/pen weapons.
Clothes shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/clothes_shop.c)
   Sells low ac armours (i.e. pants, etc.)
Basket shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/basket_shop.c)
   Sells baskets (i.e. containers)
Liquor shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/liquor_shop.c)
   Sells liquors.
Rope shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/cliffside/ropeshop1.c)
   Sells ropes (Part of a quest)
Jewel shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/jewel_shop.c)
   Sells relatively expensive jewels (Role-playing purpose only)
Wine shop - (/d/Kalad/common/trade/tsquare/wine_shop.c)
   Sells wines & liquor.

CENTRAL DISTRICT
_______________________________________________________________
